(the man who came to dinner) and yea the breakfast club thing never worked out but thats life right? hmmmmm i wish i had a fish....id call it Bubbles, or Ralph, ooo or ummmm Mr. Scales......yep an dhe would be my friend. hmmm im a boring/random person.....Golly Be Willikers!!!!! im a loser....well thats ok i like being a loser!!! im awesome and thats ok. hmmm i finished my A.D.D. test today. i couldnt finish it before because i was distracted.....but the physcologist said i did "well" but watever she means by "well"  i really dont know but thats ok!! hmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm....done.

i heart u kimmy!!!

ladies and gentlemen, HOMEWORK SUCKS!!! i have a project due tomorrow and i hardly started. my friend is trying to convince me to masturbate and "NO" is my final answer!!! do i win 1 million bucks?  damn. well yea ummmmm i hate ingraham high school, well it has its ups and downs but im a happy monkey. today the word "fish" kept popping up in my conversations with my fellow students. and im still asking myself "how the hell did i get this word stuck into my conversations?" but the thing is that i just say "fish" randomly and dont know why. well ummmm  yea have a nice day kids!!!
